            alt="Joanna Perry, mortgage broker and founder of The Loan Lady Club, serving Sacramento and Northern California. NMLS 243348."
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl"
          />
          <p
            class="mt-4 text-xs"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: rgba(44, 44, 44, 0.6);"
          >
            Official profile of Joanna Perry, NMLS 243348. Licensed mortgage broker serving clients throughout California and multiple states. Counties served include Placer, Sacramento, El Dorado, Yuba, Yolo, and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Text -->
        <div>
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-4 leading-tight"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Joanna Perry
          </h1>
          <p
            class="text-base md:text-lg mb-4"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Mortgage Broker | Founder, The Loan Lady Club | NMLS 243348
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            I have spent 15 plus years learning every corner of the mortgage industry so that you do not have to figure it out alone. My job is not to sell you a loan. My job is to educate you, protect you, and make sure you make the best decision for your family.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Bio and Career Story -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background-color: #F5F0E8;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6"
        style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
      >
        A Career Built From the Ground Up
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
        style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
      >
        Joanna Perry earned a finance degree from Sacramento State University and began her career in consumer lending, working through every operational role in the industry including credit underwriting, closing, notary services, loan servicing, and payment collection. She went on to work as a mortgage banker at Wells Fargo Home Mortgage, gaining institutional experience across multiple branches and loan programs. She later moved to a smaller retail company to access a broader range of products, where she recognized that big banks limit what their loan officers can offer. In 2008, when the housing market collapsed, Joanna stayed in the industry and built her business on a simple principle: people over profits. Today, The Loan Lady Club operates entirely on referrals. No paid advertising. No cold calls. Just clients who trust her enough to send their families and friends.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: What Makes Joanna Different -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4"
          style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
        >
          What Makes Joanna Different
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div
          class="p-6 rounded-md h-full"
          style="background-color: #F5F0E8; border: 1px solid #E8E2D9;"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Pre-Underwriting Before You Shop
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Joanna completely underwrites your loan file before you begin shopping for a home. This is not standard industry practice. It means no surprises after you are already in contract, have paid deposits, and scheduled inspections.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div
          class="p-6 rounded-md h-full"
          style="background-color: #F5F0E8; border: 1px solid #E8E2D9;"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Education First
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Every client receives a thorough education on their options, their numbers, and their strategy before any decisions are made. You will never feel rushed or pushed toward a product.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div
          class="p-6 rounded-md h-full"
          style="background-color: #F5F0E8; border: 1px solid #E8E2D9;"
