            Broker Access
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            As an independent broker with access to both wholesale and traditional banking channels, Joanna is not limited to one lender's products. She shops the market on your behalf.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div
          class="p-6 rounded-md h-full"
          style="background-color: #F5F0E8; border: 1px solid #E8E2D9;"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Built on Trust, Not Advertising
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C;"
          >
            Many clients come through a referral from someone they trust—and others find us through search, social media, or word of mouth. However you found your way here, you are welcome. There is no cold outreach, no paid ads, no pressure. Reach out and let's start a conversation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Homes for Heroes Affiliation -->
