            I joined Homes for Heroes because so many of the families I work with spend their lives serving others. Teachers, nurses, first responders, and military families carry an incredible amount of responsibility, and they deserve a home-buying experience that is honest, respectful, and financially protective. This program allows me to give something meaningful back while helping people make smart, confident decisions about their future.
          </p>

